Racemod client UI + HUD data, vendored for the client-download pk3.

Upstream: https://github.com/DenMSC/racemod_data
Commit:   9aa3560a82cc4adcd7e8adb215f2fc205bfda40e (2024-04-02)

Contents: the "Racemod Options" gametype menu (ui/porkui/racemod_main.rml and
friends) plus the ale_racemod HUD and strafe-arrow assets. Packaged by the
server Dockerfile into racemod_ui_v4_local_21pure.pk3 — the *21pure name makes
it explicit-pure, so with sv_pure 1 clients are offered it for download
automatically (it contains no native libraries, which clients would refuse).
